```json
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "title": "School Timetable",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "schoolName": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "academicYear": {
      "type": "string",
      "pattern": "^\\d{4}-\\d{4}$"
    },
    "classes": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "className": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "teacher": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "teacherId": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "teacherName": {
                "type": "string"
              }
            },
            "required": [ "teacherId", "teacherName" ]
          },
          "schedule": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "day": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "enum": ["Monday", "Tuesday", "Wednesday", "Thursday", "Friday"]
                },
                "startTime": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "pattern": "^([0-1]?[0-9]|2[0-3]):[0-5][0-9]$"
                },
                "endTime": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "pattern": "^([0-1]?[0-9]|2[0-3]):[0-5][0-9]$"
                }
              },
              "required": [ "day", "startTime", "endTime" ]
            }
          }
        },
        "required": [ "className", "teacher", "schedule" ]
      }
    }
  },
  "required": [ "schoolName", "academicYear", "classes" ]
}
```

### Explanation

1. **`schoolName`**: The name of the school.
2. **`academicYear`**: The academic year in the format "YYYY-YYYY".
3. **`classes`**: An array of class objects. Each class is an object that contains:
    - **`className`**: The name of the class or subject.
    - **`teacher`**: An object representing the teacher with:
      - **`teacherId`**: The unique ID of the teacher.
      - **`teacherName`**: The name of the teacher.
    - **`schedule`**: An array of schedule objects. Each schedule object includes:
      - **`day`**: The day of the week.
      - **`startTime`**: The start time of the class in 24-hour format (HH:MM).
      - **`endTime`**: The end time of the class in 24-hour format (HH:MM).

